[SPAM Fried Rice Burger~ Collaboration with Goh Joo Hin Pte Ltd #Ciruitbreaker package]
🍳
Why go out when you can have the best fried rice right at home?
Here is the easy fried rice with leftover rice, SPAM, Mili Green Peas, Mili Corn, fluffy eggs and a nice kick of garlic and red chili padi, better than take out and so easy to make!
For seasoning, I only use liquid amino soy sauce, a dash of white pepper and salt. 
Swipe picture to ⬅️ to watch the cooking video.
.
🛒Bundle Promo from 18 to 24 May with @qoo10sg 
Buy 4 x SPAM Less Sodium, free 2 x @newmoonsg Laksa Paste .
